test_cont_loop_countdown

: test_cont_loop_countup
  8 0 1 +loop: ind cont end \ Should terminate.
  T{ ind <T> 8 }T

  T{
    8 0 1
    +loop: ind
      ind 5 < if cont end
      leave
    end
    ind
  <T>
    5
  }T
;
test_cont_loop_countup

